
Install and run on Ubuntu 14.04
-------------------------------

Install dependancies:

  sudo aptitude install ruby2.0-dev ruby-gstreamer
  sudo ruby2.0 /usr/bin/gem install sinatra sinatra-contrib data_mapper dm-sqlite-adapter sqlite3


Run:

  ruby2.0 main.rb


Create a test RTP stream to a localhost port 5004:

  curl --request PUT --data-binary '{"dst_host":"localhost","dst_port":5004}' http://localhost:4567/streams/test
